data.description: Welcome to the highly desirable neighborhood of Waterford's Edge, where an exciting opportunity awaits to own this stunning new construction 2-story home. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, this spacious residence offers ample space and modern features for comfortable living.  Step inside and be greeted by the commercial-grade luxury vinyl laminate flooring that flows throughout the first floor, exuding both style and durability. Wall-to-wall carpeting on the second floor adds warmth and comfort to the bedrooms.  The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring LED lighting that illuminates the space and enhances the ambiance. Enjoy the elegance of granite countertops, complemented by soft-close white shaker cabinets that provide ample storage. Two island lights create a focal point, while a deep stainless sink with a sprayer adds convenience. The kitchen island also features a cozy breakfast nook, perfect for casual dining.  On the main floor, you'll find a versatile den/office space that can easily be transformed into a fourth bedroom, providing flexibility to suit your needs.  The master bedroom is a serene retreat, complete with a set of double French doors, two closets (including a walk-in closet), and a ceiling fan for added comfort. The master bathroom offers a touch of luxury with its double sinks and a privacy stand-up shower lined with Mediterranean-style luxury tile.  Two of the bedrooms share a "Jack & Jill" bathroom, providing convenience and privacy for family members or guests. For added convenience, washer and dryer hookups are available both in the basement and on the first floor.  Situated on almost a quarter acre, this home is surrounded by fencing, offering privacy and security. The town has already approved the addition of a garage, allowing you to customize the home to your liking.  The full, unfinished basement with a walkout presents an excellent opportunity to expand the living space. With approximately 849 sq. feet available, there is potential to create additional rooms and add approximately 256 sq. ft. of usable space.  This home has a fascinating story, originally designed for a beachfront property in Union Beach but ended up in Atco. Imagine bringing the beach ambiance to Atco with your spacious, fenced-in backyard, which is nearly a quarter of an acre and large enough to accommodate an in-ground pool. This home offers unique characteristics, including sliders, walkouts, and more. With the right buyer and price point, the seller is open to modifying the home to make it perfect for you. Don't hesitate to negotiate!  Waterford's Edge is a highly sought-after neighborhood, and this home presents a wonderful opportunity to make it your own. Let's come together and turn this house into your dream home. Schedule your showing today and seize the chance to make this beautiful property your own!
